ctory","group":"Settings","lastEventId":null},{"lastDataType":6,"lastValue":null,"controlType":"text","lastChangedByWidgetId":null,"lastExecutionContext":null,"helpText":"The user id to identify this user/sesion.","controlSettings":{"group":"Settings","placeholder":"Enter text"},"name":"Settings.User_Id","group":"Settings","lastEventId":null},{"lastDataType":6,"lastValue":true,"controlType":"anything","lastChangedByWidgetId":null,"lastExecutionContext":{"eventId":3,"currentPath":["{#}DjpN:3","{#}3h8uNyc"]},"helpText":"Linked to the 'abort' ports of all agents","controlSettings":{"value":null},"name":"Settings.Abort_All_Processing","group":"Settings","lastEventId":null},{"lastDataType":5,"lastValue":{"id":"tool_WriteFile_Pilva5IVsanOV3GqdtGT","type":"function","function":{"name":"WriteFile","arguments":"{\"filePath\":\"\",\"fileName\":\"conversation_history.json\",\"contents\":\"{\\n  \\\"metadata\\\": {\\n    \\\"total_turns\\\": 3,\\n    \\\"last_updated\\\": \\\"2026-04-09T10:15:20Z\\\"\\n  },\\n  \\\"turns\\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\\"agent\\\": \\\"Researcher\\\",\\n      \\\"timestamp\\\": \\\"2026-04-09T09:05:00Z\\\",\\n      \\\"action\\\": \\\"research_complete\\\",\\n      \\\"message\\\": \\\"Initial research completed.\\\"\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"agent\\\": \\\"User\\\",\\n      \\\"timestamp\\\": \\\"2026-04-09T10:14:00Z\\\",\\n      \\\"action\\\": \\\"redo_request\\\",\\n      \\\"message\\\": \\\"redo research\\\"\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"agent\\\": \\\"Researcher\\\",\\n      \\\"timestamp\\\": \\\"2026-04-09T10:15:20Z\\\",\\n      \\\"action\\\": \\\"research_complete\\\",\\n      \\\"message\\\": \\\"Research RE-COMPLETED. Fields captured: 8/8. Source: merged. Focus on interdisciplinary rankings and school-specific hub intelligence.\\\"\\n    }\\n  ]\\n}\"}"}},"controlType":"anything","lastChangedByWidgetId":null,"lastExecutionContext":{"eventId":9,"currentPath":["{#}DjpN:9","{#}3h8uNyc","{#}dMEiF95","{#}3h8uNyc","{#}gt2l79i","{#}7J449xJ","{#}b9L7wFM"]},"helpText":"Routes tool scanning events to all agent tools.","controlSettings":{"value":null},"name":"Settings.Scan _Tools","group":"Settings","lastEventId":null},{"lastDataType":1,"lastValue":"/Users/piny/JobApp/workspace/workspace/cv_assembly_state.json","controlType":"text","lastChangedByWidgetId":null,"lastExecutionContext":null,"controlSettings":{"value":"","placeholder":"Enter text"},"name":"Settings.NewCV_Path","group":"Settings","lastEventId":null},{"lastDataType":1,"lastValue":"# ✓ Researcher Complete\n\nCompany intelligence re-gathered for **The University of Melbourne**.\n\n- **Research quality:** RESEARCH_COMPLETE\n- **Data source:** merged (Company specific + Sector archetype)\n- **Fields captured:** 8/8\n- **Hiring Unit Identified:** School of Physics\n\n**Key Insights:**\n- **Culture:** Shift towards 'Scientific Imagination' and 'One Team, One Vision', heavily focused on breaking down interdisciplinary barriers (as evidenced by 2026 THE Rankings).\n- **Leadership:** Current interim leadership under Professor Glyn Davis AC; focus on agility and growth in the Quantum science research capacity.\n- **Hiring Unit:** The School of Physics is prioritising the 'Balanced Academic' profile (45% Research / 40% Teaching) with specific curriculum development needs for 'Quantum Systems'.\n\n**Sources:**\n1. [Times Higher Education Interdisciplinary Science Rankings 2026](https://www.linkedin.com/posts/-schmidt-science-fellows_2026-interdisciplinary-science-rankings-define-activity-7397199135449440256-bNq1) _(company)_\n2. [Quantum on the Cusp—What to Prepare for in the Emerging Ecosystem](https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/quantum-cuspwhat-prepare-emerging-ecosystem-tech-computing-brooks-uzage) _(company)_\n3. [University Leadership Activity - Thas Nirmalathas](https://au.linkedin.com/in/thas-nirmalathas) _(company)_\n4. [Lecturer or Senior Lecturer in Quantum Physics - Sector Standards](https://www.quantiki.org/position/lecturer-or-senior-lecturer-quantum-physics) _(sector)_\n5. [Higher Education Enterprise Agreement (Probation Standards)](https://cpsunsw.org.au/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/University-of-Sydney-Enterprise-Agreement-2023-2026.pdf) _(sector)_\n\n**Next:** JD Enhancer will analyse and enrich the job description using this new intelligence.\n\n---\n\nSend any message to continue.","controlType":"anything","lastChangedByWidgetId":null,"lastExecutionContext":{"eventId":64,"currentPath":["{#}DjpN:9","{#}3h8uNyc","{#}dMEiF95","{#}3h8uNyc","{#}gt2l79i","{#}7J449xJ"]},"controlSettings":{"value":null},"name":"AgentOutput","group":null,"lastEventId":null},{"lastDataType":1,"lastValue":"**Initiating Investigation Protocol**\n\nI'm now diving into the research phase. I've accessed the project memory and am extracting key company details and the target job description to pinpoint the hiring unit. Initial findings are promising; the focus is sharpening.\n\n\n**Restarting Data Acquisition**\n\nI'm restarting the file reading process. I'll read project\\_memory.json to grasp the company and position, along with the sector. Simultaneously, I'll extract the core elements from jd\\_raw.txt to identify the hiring unit. The aim is to swiftly move to the research phase as defined by the protocol.\n\n\n**Reviewing the Scope**\n\nI'm now zeroing in on the research parameters. My priority is to understand the user's need to \"redo research,\" given my role in gathering company intelligence for job applications. I've re-read the project metadata to solidify my focus, starting with the University of Melbourne and the targeted position.\n\n\n**Commencing the Execution**\n\nI'm moving forward with the plan. I've successfully identified the target company, position, and sector, and I've read the relevant documents. Now, I'm ready to execute the research tools: `ResearchCompany` and `ResearchSector`. My next step is to merge the outputs and synthesize them into the required fields, followed by a validation check. Finally, I will update the memory and log the progress.\n\n\n**Restarting the Investigation**\n\nI'm restarting the research phase. I'm focusing on gathering the latest company and sector intel, aiming to refine the data collection process from the ground up, to ensure optimal data quality and coverage.\n\n\n**Reworking the Synthesis**\n\nI'm now integrating the synthesis of the eight required fields. I'm prioritizing the `mission_values` and `culture_overview` fields, drawing initial insights from both the ResearchCompany results and the job description. The goal is to craft a comprehensive summary of the institution's values and work environment.\n\n\n**Consolidating the Results**\n\nI'm now integrating the synthesized findings. I've focused on `mission_values` and `culture_overview`, leveraging insights from both company and job description documents. My next steps involve consolidating the remaining fields, incorporating recent developments and strategic initiatives. I'll then move to validation.\n\n\n**Analyzing the \"Redo\" Request**\n\nI'm revisiting the initial request to \"redo research\". I've re-examined the outputs from `ResearchCompany` and `ResearchSector`. Recognizing the need to start fresh, even if the information seems similar, I'm now proceeding with the synthesis phase, as instructed, which is the heart of the re-execution process.\n\n\n**Confirming Data Synthesis**\n\nI'm now fully immersed in the synthesis phase, taking a fresh look at the `ResearchCompany` and `ResearchSector` results. I've re-evaluated the initial request and determined the \"redo\" necessitates a complete data regeneration. I'm focusing on the eight key fields, ensuring each accurately reflects the latest tool outputs, particularly `mission_values` and `culture_overview`.\n\n\n**Summarizing the Findings**\n\nI'm synthesizing the fields from the most recent tool outputs, updating each according to the new `ResearchCompany` and `ResearchSector` results. I am now finalizing the details for `interview_focus` and `hiring_unit_intelligence`, ensuring they align with the new data. Subsequently, I'll update the `project_memory.json` with a timestamp.\n\n\n**Executing Final Updates**\n\nI'm now writing the updated `project_memory.json`, `agent_reasoning.json`, and `conversation_history.json` files. My final assessment, reflecting the \"redo\" requirement, involves a precise regeneration of the eight key fields, using only the newest tool outputs. All necessary source attributions have been included.\n\n\n","controlType":"anything","lastChangedByWidgetId":null,"lastExecutionContext":{"eventId":65,"currentPath":["{#}DjpN:9","{#}3h8uNyc","{#}dMEiF95","{#}3h8uNyc","{#}gt2l79i","{#}7J449xJ"]},"controlSettings":{"value":null},"name":"AgentReasoning","group":null,"lastEventId":null},{"lastDataType":5,"lastValue":{"finish_reason":"stop","native_finish_reason":"STOP","usage":{"prompt_tokens":20039,"completion_tokens":490,"total_tokens":20529,"cost":0.00970795,"is_byok":false,"prompt_tokens_details":{"cached_tokens":3959,"cache_write_tokens":0,"audio_tokens":0,"video_tokens":0},"cost_details":{"upstream_inference_cost":0.00970795,"upstream_inference_prompt_cost":0.00823795,"upstream_inference_completions_cost":0.00147},"completion_tokens_details":{"reasoning_tokens":0,"image_tokens":0,"audio_tokens":0}}},"controlType":"anything","lastChangedByWidgetId":null,"lastExecutionContext":{"eventId":66,"currentPath":["{#}DjpN:9","{#}3h8uNyc","{#}dMEiF95","{#}3h8uNyc","{#}gt2l79i","{#}7J449xJ"]},"controlSettings":{"value":null},"name":"AgentDebug","group":null,"lastEventId":null}],"author":{"firstName":"Piny","lastName":"Amum","id":"kuser_ixy9tcyd8q062njpvhih"}}